{
  "stem": "2916.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he kept measuring this way and that way and the length of the nose.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I, again, made it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was in this superior group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was given this very responsible, very carefully supervised job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I really wasn't up to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took time until I learned it, and I was always in a panic that I should make a mistake because if you make a mistake, you could be very badly penalized.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because of my physical appearance, I was deemed highly intelligent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And unfortunately, that gave me a very, very big burden to carry, burden of a very sophisticated job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we were up to the point where we were shipped from Augsburg to one of the subsidiary camps of Dachau.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The understanding was that the allied front is approaching, and they are concentrating the inmates.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were brought to a camp called Muehldorf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Muehldorf-- near Muehldorf, there was a cement factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And most of the-- mostly men were there, in Muehldorf.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't meet any women when we arrived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard that among the men is also my brother from people-- you know, again, very quickly, how do you find these things out?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because as soon as you arrive, the men on the other side of the fence-- you know, there was this barbed wire fence-- come to the fence, and they shout, where do you come from?",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you shout the name of the town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- you ask them, where do you come from?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then by the name of the town, they would ask, is so-and-so among you?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we say, is so-and-so among you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, I heard that there are men from Somorja.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we said, is Mark Friedman, Markus-- my father-- is he there?",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
